  <view class="guize_1_top3">
    <text class="guize_1_text2">1.授权登录</text>
  </view>
  <view class="guize_1_top2">
    <text class="guize_1_text3">1）用户登录小程序并授权使用微信头像及昵称，且登录手机号（一个微信号一次）+100积分；</text>
  </view>

  <view class="guize_1_top3">
    <text class="guize_1_text2">2.购买项目</text>
  </view>
  <view class="guize_1_top2">
