  </view>
  <view class="guize_1_top4">
    <text class="guize_1_text3">2）若项目无尾款，积分及时到账，若项目有尾款，尾款支付成功后积分到账；</text>
  </view>

  <view class="guize_1_top3">
    <text class="guize_1_text2">3.邀请好友购买项目</text>
  </view>
  <view class="guize_1_top2">
    <text class="guize_1_text3">1）被邀请者购买项目且使用后，邀请人+500积分，无上限；</text>
  </view>
  <view class="guize_1_top4">
    <text class="guize_1_text3">2）被邀请人需为小程序的新用户；</text>
  </view>
  <view class="guize_1_top4">
    <text class="guize_1_text3">3）被邀请人需在邀请人链接内购买商品；</text>
  </view>
  <view class="guize_1_top4">
    <text class="guize_1_text3">4）链接有效时间为5天；</text>
  </view>


  <view class="guize_1_top3">
    <text class="guize_1_text2">4.邀请好友登录</text>
  </view>
  <view class="guize_1_top2">
    <text class="guize_1_text3">1）每邀请1位用户+100积分；</text>
  </view>
  <view class="guize_1_top4">
    <text class="guize_1_text3">2）若累计分享给5位用户，可额外+100积分；每日一次；</text>
  </view>
  <view class="guize_1_top4">
    <text class="guize_1_text3">3）被邀请人需在邀请者邀请的小程序内登录小程序并授权使用微信头像及昵称，且登录手机号；</text>
  </view>
  <view class="guize_1_top4">
